review: Elizabeth was great with my 6 month old daughter. The only issue was that she was about 30 minutes late.
Petra taught me great tricks and tips on how to sleep train my fussy 6 month old daughter.
My 2 children loved Catherine! They could not stop raving baout how fun she was.
Jenny took my kids on an adventure of a lifetime! They told me they had a very busy day, which I love when my children are active. Plus they fell asleep so quickly the day she babysat!
My kids loved Serena, they loved coloring and painting with her.
I caught Simona on her phone a little to often for my liking...
Jackie was nice, kids loved her. What more can I say.
Emma was nice! She was very patient with my toddler.
Tyler was cool. I really liked her and my toddler seemed to as well. Will be booking again!
So impressed with what Kylie brings to the table.
